data.description: This home is the cute Move-In-Ready home that you've been looking for. On a .25 acre lot there is plenty of space for all you want to do. Wonderfully maintained with a New stucco exterior, newer roof, newer HVAC, original wood floors, dual pane windows, ceiling fans, RV access and RV parking on both sides of the home along with a huge backyard that would be perfect for a pool, play structure, garden, you name it. Close to shopping, restaurants, along with quick access to Hwy 80 and just minutes to down town Sac or Roseville.
